LARGE PORTION OF THE COMPANY'S NET SALES IS DERIVED FROM ITS INTERNATIONAL OPERATIONS. ALSO, A MAJORITY OF THE RAW MATERIALS USED IN THE COMPANY'S PRODUCTS IS OBTAINED FROM SOURCES OUTSIDE OF THE

